overview: Maud is spurred to do anything to stay and cling to her last shred of fame. Exploiting the will of fickle consumers and the few who care personally, Maud finds the lines between the online void and reality increasingly blurred as she crawls back to the top.
tagline: I wanted to be just like you, but then i realised even you don't know who you are
title: The Stallion House
